---
---

<section class="relative w-full">
  <!-- SVG Shape at bottom -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-[100px] -z-10">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-full">
      <path class="fill-secondary" d="M0,6V0h1000v100L0,6z"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-[1020px] px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-0 py-16 lg:py-24">
      <!-- Left Column - Content -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
        <h4 class="font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
          About Real World PDR
        </h4>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-text leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Real World PDR was born from the desire to teach people who want to get into the Paintless Dent Repair industry how to provide the best possible service to their customers.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We don't just show you how to repair a dent in a lab. We want you to be confident that the skills you learn with us Real World PDR will translate to real life.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            PDR is not easy, it will require a lot of practice and patience. But we're with you every step of the way, from what tools you need to buy, all the way through the most advanced dents and creases.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="https://realworldpdr.com/real-world-pdr-courses/" 
            class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors duration-200 hover:scale-105 transform transition-transform"
          >
            See Courses
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Spacer (hidden on mobile) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="h-32"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
